{"tid":2504048,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"原來以前公開考試有政治科，要批評中共唔代表人民利益","createTime":"2021-04-25T14:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T15:19:10.000Z","uid":146454,"like":158,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ad121a1debe74f9d14308efa26f2aeeb36bf4c","tid":2504048,"uid":146454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"原來當年CE 同 A-Level 都有一科叫<strong>政府與公共事務 (Government &amp; public affairs)</strong>，要考生研究中共同埋香港嘅政治體制<br />\n本身以為九七淪陷之後，試卷會因為政治審查而限制尺度，點之唔係<br />\n<br />\n例如呢份係2010年A-Level試題<br />\n試題要討論釋法點樣破壞法治、區議會應否全部直選、法治同司法獨立如何保障人權<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUbbC3dcTdfHpieHnC4CZkokDtc75Efjyg3DHXEPXcy72?filename=wOCMO6V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwOCMO6V.png&h=c68ecf01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n而答案都冇限制考生政治取態同價值<br />\n我用Q.11題目個參考答案做例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNPBNwyeAbcV7namjpJQiSUo7nVMqbG5Tw1VzykgEUB14?filename=6vhth1N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6vhth1N.png&h=c6ee6bd0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYQ5RQiZsHeEf1vaHArH4TBhc7SRbSPwysPeNdWZ8dLZs?filename=AwSQwmN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAwSQwmN.png&h=44697248&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n相信如果2021年DSE，答案認為親共選舉委員會毫無代表性、破壞政府管治合法性，建議中央減少干預香港，考官應該會被革職兼取消試題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而關於討論中共政制的部分就仲癲<br />\n例如呢題(2003 CE Paper 1 Q5)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢題(2004 CE Paper 1 Q2)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有呢題(2010 CE Paper 1 Q3)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一個地方係咪自由，可以由公開試卷設題、考生答案、官方答案反映出黎</strong><br />\n最後呢科部分課程就併入左今日通識科<br />\n而通識科亦會係不久之後取消，仲要考生背固定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />答案<br />\n而今日政府可以干預出題自由、考生要擔心係試題批評政府後會被秋後算帳，<br />\n只能係呢度立此存照，話比後人知，香港以前曾經都有一定自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/sigh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/sigh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a0d59f60f5474b67c6f1287aba1c9d2c24c3bf","tid":2504048,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T14:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82a9dbe64155b87eea27bd87b4bcb8f04cf07bb","tid":2504048,"uid":146454,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T14:19:27.000Z","msg":"點樣搵到當年試題?<br />\n<a href=\"https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/web/guest/hkcee-and-hkale-papers-collection\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmis.hkpl.gov.hk%2Fweb%2Fguest%2Fhkcee-and-hkale-papers-collection&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepG%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=4fda0c95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/web/guest/hkcee-and-hkale-papers-collection</a><br />\n呢個資料庫有曬所有A-Level 同 CE 試題<br />\n我會建議大家Back-up<br />\n可能有日成科試題都會被ban access"},{"pid":"df7cb9f575c72b7717bdd0526505c8063a918729","tid":2504048,"uid":146454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a82a9dbe64155b87eea27bd87b4bcb8f04cf07bb","tid":2504048,"uid":146454,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T14:19:27.000Z","msg":"點樣搵到當年試題?<br />\n<a href=\"https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/web/guest/hkcee-and-hkale-papers-collection\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmis.hkpl.gov.hk%2Fweb%2Fguest%2Fhkcee-and-hkale-papers-collection&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepG%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=4fda0c95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/web/guest/hkcee-and-hkale-papers-collection</a><br />\n呢個資料庫有曬所有A-Level 同 CE 試題<br />\n我會建議大家Back-up<br />\n可能有日成科試題都會被