e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T15:59:48.000Z","msg":"下面我會按議題 講下我覺得有意思嘅題目<br />\n<strong>採訪與新聞自由</strong><br />\n<br />\n呢題係common sense 題目 答案係B (2008 CE Paper 2 Q28)<br />\n但係今日香港政府都開始審查新聞<br />\n至於選項D...望翻蔡玉玲單案 就會發覺正常新聞報導都會中刑責<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/sigh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條(2003 CE Paper 1 Q4) 就預言警察會設立記者區 限制記者採訪權力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條(2009 CE Paper 1 Q3) 討論香港電台的功能<br />\n李百全上任之前港台係Fufill 題目入面反對一方嘅理據<br />\n李百全上任之後港台就變成官媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40428c8bbca138bb53a945dd52967370de254981","tid":2504048,"uid":134774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T16:03:43.000Z","msg":"等睇幾個月後政府清算出題果d教師同考評局職員同吊銷牌照"},{"pid":"dc6ff970f28570dde56390f182f4c925ccf1a13f","tid":2504048,"uid":146454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T16:10:36.000Z","msg":"呢條(2005 CE Paper 1 Q3)就討論新聞自由的重要性同埋限制<br />\n如果擺翻今日成條題目再問過 又用呢參考答案做答案 <br />\n應該會不合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條(2011 AL Paper 1 Q7) 就討論當年傳媒面對限制<br />\n主要係自我審查同埋中資滲透 <br />\n望翻今日只能話低處未算低<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab31b50cf6070215c2dba77a3b9814e730b1dac","tid":2504048,"uid":146454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da2bb0692222fb9f086ad9f270b3e3d1ccd59d6d","tid":2504048,"uid":126325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"我記得啲人Repeat AL時，會自修ASL哩科<br />\n用黎報Poly屈分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}